commandList:
There is no gate, no lock, no bolt that you can set upon the freedom of my mind:
 - To set up a writing sprint for y minutes in x minutes' time, type '!sprint in x for y'
- To cancel a sprint, type '!cancel sprint'. Only the person who started the sprint, or someone with the manage messages permission, can do this
 - To opt-in to a sprint that's running, type '!sprinting'
 - To be notified of every sprint, type '!sprint role'
 - To stop being notified of every sprint, type '!remove sprint role'
 - To get synonyms for a word, type '!synonym [word]'
 - To get antonyms for a word, type '!antonym [word]'
 - To get rhymes for a word, type '!rhyme [word]'
 - To find words associated with a word, type '!related [word]'
 - To find adjectives to describe a noun, type '!describe [word]'
 - To get an interesting photo for inspiration, type '!inspiration'
 - Need tech support? Type !woolf support
 - To invite this bot to another server, visit <https: //discordapp.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=364771016523907072&scope=bot&permissions=268435456>
